    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839710/extras/44cc5f1e424cd98d4adb96f75960d46c.poster.avif?t=1740229727\" width=600 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839710/extras/44cc5f1e424cd98d4adb96f75960d46c.webm?t=1740229727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839710/extras/44cc5f1e424cd98d4adb96f75960d46c.mp4?t=1740229727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alchemists is a Co-Op horror game that can be played with at least a minimum of 1 and a maximum of 4 players. Your goal is to expel the evil spirit from cursed places by completing the 4 Element ritual. Destroy the monster alone or with your team using your tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839710/extras/0d8dcc5eb7ab44c093e0f11979301a2c.poster.avif?t=1740229727\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839710/extras/0d8dcc5eb7ab44c093e0f11979301a2c.webm?t=1740229727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839710/extras/0d8dcc5eb7ab44c093e0f11979301a2c.mp4?t=1740229727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the excitement of the game with realistic graphics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839710/extras/244418ef4d5fcd943057ffa2e87a59dc.poster.avif?t=1740229727\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839710/extras/244418ef4d5fcd943057ffa2e87a59dc.webm?t=1740229727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839710/extras/244418ef4d5fcd943057ffa2e87a59dc.mp4?t=1740229727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple maps are with you to play. Trasmoz, Abandoned School, Demon Village ( Farm House coming soon)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
